ントされているクリーチャーのパワーが４以上である場合、アラクナスの蜘蛛の巣を破壊する。','Encantar criatura£A criatura encantada não pode atacar nem bloquear e suas habilidades ativadas não podem ser ativadas.£No início da etapa final, se o poder da criatura encantada for maior ou igual a 4, destrua Teia de Aracnus.','Зачаровать существо£Зачарованное существо не может атаковать или блокировать, и его активируемые способности нельзя активировать.£В начале заключительного шага, если сила зачарованного существа равна 4 или больше, уничтожьте Паутину Арахнуса.','Encantar criatura.£La criatura encantada no puede atacar o bloquear, y no pueden activarse sus habilidades activadas.£Al comienzo de tu paso final, si la fuerza de la criatura encantada es 4 o más, destruye la Red de aracnus.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('220078','Arbalest Elite','M12','Creature — Human Archer','U','{2}{W}{W}','4','2','3',NULL,'{2}{W}, {T}: Arbalest Elite deals 3 damage to target attacking or blocking creature. Arbalest Elite doesn''t untap during your next untap step.','#_There are few things as satisfying as a good, healthy thunk._#',NULL,'Chris Rahn','5','1.788','£9/22/2011: If the creature is an illegal target when Arbalest Elite’s ability tries to resolve, the ability won’t resolve and none of its effects will happen. Arbalest Elite will untap during its controller’s next untap step.£9/22/2011: If another player controls Arbalest Elite during your next untap step, the part of the effect that keeps it from untapping does nothing. It won’t try to apply during a future untap step.','W',NULL,'0.01','0.2','1.9',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','弹簧弩精兵','彈簧弩精兵','Arbalestrier d''élite','Arbalestenelite','Balestriere Scelto','大石弓の精鋭','Elite de Arbaleste','Элитные Арбалетчики','Élite de arbalestrilla',NULL,'生物～人类／弓箭手','生物～人類／弓箭手','Créature : humain et archer','Kreatur — Mensch, Bogenschütze','Creatura — Arciere Umano','クリーチャー ― 人間・射手','Criatura — Humano Arqueiro',