ional costs for the copy. However, effects based on any additional costs that were paid for the original spell are copied as though those same costs were paid for the copy too. For example, if a player sacrifices a 3/3 creature to cast Fling, and you copy it with Reverberate, the copy of Fling will also deal 3 damage to its target.£8/15/2010: If the copy says that it affects “you,” it affects the controller of the copy, not the controller of the original spell. Similarly, if the copy says that it affects an “opponent,” it affects an opponent of the copy’s controller, not an opponent of the original spell’s controller.','R',NULL,'0.63','0.95','2.5',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','令其回响','令其回響','Réverbérer','Nachhallen','Riverberare','余韻','Reverberar','Реверберация','Reverberar',NULL,'瞬间','瞬間','Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント','Mágica Instantânea','Мгновенное заклинание','Instantáneo',NULL,'复制目标瞬间或法术咒语。 你可以为该复制选择新的目标。','複製目標瞬間或巫術咒語。 你可以為該複製選擇新的目標。','Copiez le sort d''éphémère ou de rituel ciblé. Vous pouvez choisir de nouvelles cibles pour cette copie.','Kopiere einen Spontanzauber oder eine Hexerei deiner Wahl. Du kannst neue Ziele für die Kopie bestimmen.','Copia una magia istantaneo o stregoneria bersaglio. Puoi scegliere nuovi bersagli per la copia.','インスタント呪文１つかソーサリー呪文１つを対象とし、それをコピーする。 あなたはそのコピーの新しい対象を選んでもよい。','Copie a mágica instantânea ou de feitiço alvo. Você pode escolher novos alvos para a cópia.','Скопируйте целевое мгновенное заклинание или заклинание волшебства. Вы можете выбрать новые цели для этой копии.','Copia el hechizo objetivo de instantáneo o de conjuro. Puedes elegir nuevos objetivos para la copia.',NULL,'#_每个动作总会引起更快更暴烈的回应。_#','#_每個動作總會引起更快更暴烈的回應。_#','#_Pour chaque action, il y a une réaction plus rapide et plus violente._#','#_Auf jede Aktion folgt eine prompte und gewalttätigere Reaktion._#','#_Per ogni azione, c''è una reazione più rapida e più violenta._#','#_どんな行動にも、さらに素早く強烈な反応がある。_#','#_Para cada ação há uma reação mais rápida e vio